Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.46,0:00:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻找吧  收集梦想的碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.54,0:00:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使无奈也能感受到此刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.65,0:00:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比外表看起来更单纯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.32,0:00:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却无法坦诚表达心意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.06,0:00:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是把想说的话收藏在口袋里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.43,0:00:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今更不能说出幼稚的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.74,0:00:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好说时间能解决一切 却怕无人能懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.28,0:00:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一天24小时我都相信你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.55,0:00:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注视着你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.29,0:01:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这是司空见惯的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.29,0:01:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间总是嘲笑着匆匆而过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.43,0:01:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其执着回忆 不如寻找现在的梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.19,0:01:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇  在这里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.96,0:01:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很近了  就在森林那一带
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.43,0:01:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尾随着四魂碎片的我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.63,0:01:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧遇遭到\N奈落的妖怪袭击的琥珀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.50,0:01:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落驱使妖怪取回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.94,0:01:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埋藏在琥珀体内的四魂碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.78,0:02:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.02,0:02:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜于和琥珀重逢的珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.96,0:02:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是琥珀已被奈落消除记忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.89,0:02:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法想起珊瑚的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.03,0:02:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.73,0:02:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从奈落的手里逃出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.94,0:02:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希望是如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.27,0:02:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是奈落的陷阱不会错的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.54,0:02:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信琥珀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.38,0:02:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是想要这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.48,0:02:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的我除了相信还能怎样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.05,0:02:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在这个时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.05,0:02:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,率领大群妖怪的神乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.59,0:02:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现在我们面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.42,0:02:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要取回埋藏在\N琥珀体内的四魂碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.59,0:02:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若四魂碎片被取走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.39,0:02:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀就会没命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.16,0:02:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了保护琥珀免遭那些家伙的毒手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.50,0:02:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉一行人阻止了妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.40,0:02:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我则和琥珀一起逃入森林中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.07,0:03:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望能想起那个人的一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.51,0:03:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是怎么搞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.71,0:03:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种感觉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.95,0:03:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有什么可怕的东西\N我非想起来不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.09,0:03:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了她  杀了戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.70,0:03:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破魔之矢用光了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.84,0:03:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.08,0:03:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第50话\N那张脸绝不会自心底消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.62,0:03:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞来骨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.86,0:03:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧  琥珀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.07,0:04:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝不会再把你交给奈落的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.51,0:04:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.44,0:04:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.90,0:04:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉  你听好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.70,0:04:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要尽可能牵制神乐她们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.27,0:04:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.90,0:04:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.04,0:04:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了抓个逃走的小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.84,0:04:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带了这样一大群来  这样刚好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.84,0:04:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.55,0:04:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们全被奈落的把戏唬住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.72,0:04:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好演吧  琥珀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.85,0:04:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里碰见真是百年难得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.22,0:04:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就顺便杀光你们吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.36,0:04:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.93,0:05:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的头我要定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.16,0:05:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风刃之舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.95,0:05:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.33,0:05:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.03,0:05:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和刚才琥珀完全不一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.21,0:05:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀啊  杀了戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.71,0:05:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.36,0:06:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.63,0:06:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.44,0:06:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.07,0:06:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.51,0:06:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.15,0:06:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.39,0:06:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇  琥珀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.02,0:06:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.03,0:06:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.76,0:06:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.27,0:06:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.77,0:06:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事  这点伤没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.28,0:06:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.68,0:07:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云母  跟在戈薇身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.98,0:07:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇  很痛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.29,0:07:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.69,0:07:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.80,0:07:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.56,0:07:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道珊瑚她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.50,0:07:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没完没了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.38,0:07:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风刃之舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.88,0:07:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.32,0:07:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么不拔刀啊  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.09,0:07:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对付你们不需要用铁碎牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.73,0:07:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散魂铁爪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.33,0:07:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你还没熟悉刀的用法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.17,0:07:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就使用爪子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.10,0:07:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头脑真好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.17,0:08:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.41,0:08:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.54,0:08:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉  对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.05,0:08:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.15,0:08:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少罗唆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.42,0:08:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样就用砍的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.55,0:08:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铁碎牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.93,0:08:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.03,0:08:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刀法变的这么迟钝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.03,0:08:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶…还是重的无法随心所欲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.04,0:08:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了牵制这群妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.44,0:08:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须让它们以为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.44,0:08:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀似乎还在这间屋子里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.21,0:09:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.71,0:09:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还敢看别的地方啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.51,0:09:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来屋子里是空的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.88,0:09:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是为了巧妙的拖住我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.92,0:09:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别跑  神乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.15,0:09:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还没跟我一决胜负呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.79,0:09:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.63,0:10:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要被骗了  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.06,0:10:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么  弥勒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.63,0:10:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐也好  这些妖怪也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.50,0:10:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的应该是琥珀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.14,0:10:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他们连一个人\N都没有追过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.14,0:10:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她们打算将我们困住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.18,0:10:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许被困住的反而是我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.08,0:10:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果奈落真正的目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.05,0:10:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是琥珀的话呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.72,0:10:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.16,0:10:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她追着琥珀进入森林中…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.66,0:10:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然琥珀也是奈落的手下吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.30,0:10:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在才注意到吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.37,0:10:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过已经来不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.74,0:10:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.04,0:10:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然利用琥珀对戈薇下手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.67,0:10:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.81,0:10:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个使用破魔之箭\N叫做戈薇的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.54,0:10:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常碍事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.55,0:10:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒你想做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.72,0:10:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有毒虫啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.36,0:11:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风穴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.87,0:11:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别乱来啊  弥勒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.41,0:11:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.85,0:11:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你连毒蜂也吸进去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.42,0:11:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉  你去追珊瑚还有戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.09,0:11:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.22,0:11:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  弥勒  你别死喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.49,0:11:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想逃吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.63,0:11:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要动  神乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.13,0:11:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要转个方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.30,0:11:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能连你也吸进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.37,0:11:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恕不奉陪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.78,0:11:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃掉了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.42,0:12:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒  你还好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.62,0:12:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也快点去追犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.27,0:12:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小鬼竟然装出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.90,0:12:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连虫也舍不得杀的模样来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.17,0:12:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.31,0:13:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.18,0:13:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然还没\N从奈落手里解放出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.22,0:13:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是为了伤害戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.32,0:13:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夺取四魂碎片而来的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.26,0:13:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其让你继续受到奈落的利用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.10,0:13:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我宁可…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.63,0:13:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀  我马上就让你自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.26,0:13:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.36,0:13:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让你一个人走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.00,0:13:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很快就会去陪你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.73,0:13:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.13,0:14:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.94,0:14:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉  快点去追珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.64,0:14:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不太对劲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.45,0:14:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇  你被琥珀弄伤了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.25,0:14:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮肉伤而已  而且那孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.95,0:14:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他想杀我一定做得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.66,0:14:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他却没那么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.39,0:14:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚她不知道这些事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.53,0:14:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也许打算把琥珀杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.60,0:14:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.07,0:14:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀没有一击让戈薇致命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.61,0:14:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他怎么没有遵从奈落的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.35,0:14:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.58,0:14:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使被操纵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.82,0:14:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀还残留着人类的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.21,0:15:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.95,0:15:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.58,0:15:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得不太好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.85,0:15:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么好害羞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.39,0:15:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是姐弟呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.52,0:15:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀  不要再离开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.66,0:15:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你是我弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.60,0:15:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我唯一的亲弟弟啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.04,0:15:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了你之后我也会自杀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.74,0:15:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了把你从奈落手里夺回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.48,0:15:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这么做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.88,0:15:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  琥珀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.13,0:16:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了你之后我也会自杀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.07,0:16:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了把你从奈落手里夺回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.90,0:16:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这么做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.87,0:16:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  琥珀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.28,0:16:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.27,0:16:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.78,0:16:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别阻止我  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.54,0:16:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.58,0:16:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你杀了琥珀的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.41,0:17:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只会让奈落称心如意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.85,0:17:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀  你也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.09,0:17:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不给我醒过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.91,0:17:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.94,0:17:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同命令所说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.41,0:17:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫琥珀杀了戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.11,0:17:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀绝对不会违抗奈落的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.12,0:17:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.69,0:17:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.19,0:17:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想为什么琥珀会丧失记忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.12,0:17:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是奈落操纵了他的心吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.69,0:17:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说也对  但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.13,0:17:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀自己也不愿想起往事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.93,0:17:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些不愿想起的记忆…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.08,0:18:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.42,0:18:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在琥珀面前不要再说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.92,0:18:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帐神乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.43,0:18:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本人都想忘记的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.93,0:18:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落就让他忘得一干二净
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.50,0:18:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要操纵琥珀纯洁的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.67,0:18:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对奈落而言是易如反掌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.71,0:18:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀!想起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.71,0:18:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点想起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.01,0:18:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚和驱魔师的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.99,0:18:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.19,0:18:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都给我想起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.19,0:18:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你还想活下去的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.96,0:18:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.53,0:18:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不能想起来并面对它的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.03,0:18:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的心就永远受奈落的控制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.00,0:18:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.30,0:19:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏在体内的四魂碎片会被取走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.04,0:19:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会被那家伙给杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.01,0:19:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得还真狠呢  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.39,0:19:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住  神乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.99,0:19:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是想起自己做过什么的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.99,0:19:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这小子…真的会彻底崩溃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.03,0:19:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他忘了一切的死去\N也是为了他好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.01,0:19:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.59,0:19:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  这下又…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.59,0:20:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.33,0:20:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下又回到起点了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.60,0:20:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是找麻烦的姐弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.60,0:20:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.11,0:20:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.84,0:20:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早告诉你不要那么冲动啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.28,0:20:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落那家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.45,0:20:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确命令琥珀杀了戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.35,0:20:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是琥珀却没有杀了戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.05,0:20:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他还残存着人类的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.56,0:20:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你不能杀琥珀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.13,0:20:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要把他活生生的抢回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.89,0:20:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.15,0:20:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.81,0:20:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经把你的性命延长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.15,0:20:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至让你忘记一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.49,0:21:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然没有杀了戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.99,0:21:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  琥珀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.90,0:21:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到现在你还想取回人类的心吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.10,0:21:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就试试看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.61,0:21:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将一切都回想起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.41,0:21:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  我不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.85,0:21:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.86,0:21:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就暂时再让你活一阵子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.86,0:21:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把一切都忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.14,0:21:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.88,0:22:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  那个人的脸…无法消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.57,0:22:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了真正重要的事物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.91,0:22:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若能舍弃其他一切就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.09,0:22:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而现实却是残酷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.43,0:22:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这样的时刻只要随时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.30,0:22:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭上眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.04,0:23:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑海浮现你的微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.51,0:23:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah-但愿直到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.95,0:23:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远沉睡的那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.46,0:23:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但愿你的微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.87,0:23:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永不止息存在我心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.95,0:23:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村子遭到盗贼的袭击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.72,0:23:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴虐无道的盗贼首领  蛾天丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.86,0:23:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是化成人形的蛾妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.76,0:23:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉和弥勒法师一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.70,0:23:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被困在毒茧当中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.50,0:24:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同一时刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.40,0:24:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻找犬夜叉妖化之谜的杀生丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.10,0:24:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然从老木妖怪那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.47,0:24:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得知一个恐怖的秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.61,0:24:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.28,0:24:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉的心被吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.11,0:24:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬请期待



